{"word":"H2505 - חָלַק - châlaq - khaw-lak' - Deal","slug":"H2505","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָלַק</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>châlaq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khaw-lak'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Deal"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05DC;&#x05E7; - cha&#x0302;laq</b> - <i>khaw-lak'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be smooth</i> (figuratively); by implication (as smooth stones were used for <i>lots</i>) to <i>apportion</i> or <i>separate: - </i>deal, distribute, divide, flatter, give, (have, im-) part (-ner), take away a portion, receive, separate self, (be) smooth (-er)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2506\">H2506</a>, <a href=\"#/H2509\">H2509</a>, <a href=\"#/H2510\">H2510</a>, <a href=\"#/H2511\">H2511</a>, <a href=\"#/H2512\">H2512</a>, <a href=\"#/H2513\">H2513</a>, <a href=\"#/H2514\">H2514</a>, <a href=\"#/H2519\">H2519</a>, <a href=\"#/H5555\">H5555</a>"}]}